auditorium

Class MessagePointer

  • java.lang.Object
    • auditorium.MessagePointer

  • public class MessagePointer
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents the ptr auditorium data structure. Its format is (ptr [nodeid] [sequence num] [hash]).
